Library <tt>[[cmds-menu.el]]</tt>
adds a '''Recent Commands''' submenuto the [[menu bar]] '''Tools''' menu by library <tt>[[cmds-menu.el]]</tt>.  It holds the most recent commands you have invoked using `M-x'.

Loading the library is sufficient to add the submenu, so just put this in your [[init file]]:

    (require 'cmds-menu)




----
